          <div class='quick-start-item'>Browse our course catalog and enroll in your first course</div>
          <div class='quick-start-item'>Download the EduLearn mobile app for learning on-the-go</div>
          <div class='quick-start-item'>Join our community forums and introduce yourself</div>
